Vietnamese were taking fairly heavy casualties.

37:45.015 --> 37:50.262
And I still believe that the 51st Arvin was a rather 
professional fighting force. They were

37:55.073 --> 38:03.322
reasonably well trained, even by U.S. standards, 
and they were well led.

